<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Upper left corner <rs type="material">white marble</rs> fragment from a <rs type="objectType">sarcophagus</rs> (<measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.54</measure> x <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.33</measure> visible) , partly buried; complete to left, a projection (broken) to right.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the moulding, each line on a different plane.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>Standard forms; ll.1, 3, 4, <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.02</measure>; l.2, <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.03</measure>; diairetic dots beside final <foreign lang="grc">I</foreign> in line 3.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notBefore="0101" notAfter="0300" exact="none">Second to third centuries A.D.</date>
(<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>).</p>
</div>
